  p.pad(style='font-size: 1rem;')
    | These are proejcts I have completed through tutorials and courses
    | including&nbsp;
    a(href='https://wesbos.com/courses/') Wes Bos
    |  and&nbsp;
    a(href='https://www.leveluptutorials.com/') Level Up Tutorials
